def calculate_median(arr):
    arr = sorted(arr)
    length = len(arr)
    if length % 2 != 1:
        median = arr[(length - 1) // 2]
    else:
        mid1 = arr[length // 2]
        mid2 = arr[length // 2 - 1]
        median = (mid1 + mid2) / 2
    median = round(median, 2)
    return median
